<div id="content">
							<h1 class="arc-post-title">EkoNews</h1><h3 class="arc-src">now browsing by category</h3>
				<div class="clear">&nbsp;</div>
		
				
			<div class="post-386 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-ekonews category-events category-rangers">
				<p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on October 30, 2012</p>
                <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=386">More Spooky Updates and Ranger Stuff</a></h2>
				<div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>	
				<div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/spooky-event-title1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-174" title="spooky event title1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/spooky-event-title1.png" alt="" width="347" height="110" /></a></p>
<p>Well ghostly Ekos, tomorrow is it! It is Halloween! Hope all you ghouls and goblins on the East Coast are staying safe and dry as ‘Sandy’ blows her blowy winds and rains her rainy rains on you all! Hope the sun shines for a fun day of trick or treating on October 31<sup>st</sup>!<a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/GOOD.bmp" ><img class="alignright size-full wp-image-387" title="GOOD" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/GOOD.bmp" alt="" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/halloween-house-contest.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-308" title="halloween house contest" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/halloween-house-contest.png" alt="" width="315" height="34" /></a></p>
<p>Tomorrow we will be announcing the winners of our Haunted Halloween Moon House contest – so today is really your LAST CHANCE to submit your moon houses for our consideration! Invite the managers (if their electricity hasn’t been stolen by thieving storm spirits!) to come visit your haunted homes. You can also send in screenshots of your moon houses (your Eko needs to be clearly visible in the house) to <a href="mailto:usa_blog@ekoloko.com">usa_blog@ekoloko.com</a> and don’t forget to write ‘Moon Contest’ in the subject of your mail, and your Eko name inside.</p>
<p>Good luck to all our haunted houses!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-14" title="rangers of the week header" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" alt="" width="625" height="62" /></a></p>
<p>You all know what time it is!!! It’s time to announce our newest RANGERS of the WEEK!</p>
<p>Here they are, what you’ve all been waiting for the past week, the list of Ekos who will proudly be wearing their glowing fiery halos……drum roll please….introducing:</p>
<p>SuperGal, Random132, Maxwell, hadaror, hibou123 and yuvalXD!!!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/rangers-week-5.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393" title="rangers week 5" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/rangers-week-5.png" alt="" width="575" height="201" /></a></p>
<p>And for all of you who are getting their permanent halos…or for those of you who are just interested in knowing…this week’s ceremony for Advanced Rangers will take place on two dates:</p>
<p><span style="color: #003300;"><strong>On Wednesday, October 31st, at 3:30 PM Eastern Time</strong></span> (9:30 Europe and Israel time) we will have Ido450, Ponpon5560, DanApple and maybe Taleko</p>
<p><span style="color: #003300;"><strong>On Thursday, November 1st, at 3:30 PM Eastern Time</strong></span><strong> </strong>our worthy rangers who will be getting their Advanced Ranger halos are: mrnaia, Finder92, Linkeko and maybe Taleko (who hasn’t made up his mind)</p>
<p>See you on ekoloko!</p>
				</div>
				<div class="clear"> </div>
                <div class="up-bottom-border">
				<p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=3" title="View all posts in EkoNews" rel="category">EkoNews</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=6" title="View all posts in Events" rel="category">Events</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=7" title="View all posts in Rangers" rel="category">Rangers</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=386#comments" title="Comment on More Spooky Updates and Ranger Stuff">10 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
				</div>
            
		                
                </div><!--close post class-->
	
				
			<div class="post-369 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-ekonews category-events category-lokojokes category-rangers">
				<p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on October 28, 2012</p>
                <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=369">The Halloween Event</a></h2>
				<div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>	
				<div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/spooky-event-title3.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-276" title="spooky event title3" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/spooky-event-title3.png" alt="" width="324" height="93" /></a></p>
<p>Here is some news about our Halloween Event: We have already reached our target of Koko donations!!! Great job you ghouls! And you are more than halfway there with your game scores…………</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/community-event4.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-373" title="community event4" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/community-event4.png" alt="" width="706" height="148" /></a></p>
<p>But time is running out to completely save ekoloko from Goliath Smog’s ghosts!!! <span style="color: #ff6600;"><strong>There are only 7 days left</strong></span> to continue playing our ghostly games and try and get those pumpkin-headed ghosts out of ekoloko for good!</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/community-event3.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-370" title="community event3" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/community-event3.png" alt="" width="347" height="63" /></a></p>
<p>Click the <strong>Community Event button</strong> and join us to fight the evil pumpkins sent by Goliath Smog. We need you to help us reach our targets and you’ll get cool gifts along the way so keep going Ekos! All Ekos who help us reach our goal will get the ultimate treat! So remember – you gotta be IN IT to WIN IT!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/news-title1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-13" title="news title1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/news-title1.png" alt="" width="349" height="104" /></a></p>
<p>This is not <strong>OUR</strong> Eko news but this is Cchen22’s ALMOST Eko news! So check it out:</p>
<p><a href="http://youtu.be/J8iAMZNEgf4" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://youtu.be']);">http://youtu.be/J8iAMZNEgf4</a></p>
<p>If you have things you’d like to share or send to the blog, please write to us at <a href="mailto:usa_blog@ekoloko.com">usa_blog@ekoloko.com</a> and we will be happy to include them (if we can).</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/jokes-title1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-24" title="jokes title1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/jokes-title1.png" alt="" width="250" height="87" /></a></p>
<p>Well, my sorry Ekos, since <strong>you</strong> did not come through with jokes for our corner, we got our own Megara to come up with some Halloween sillies that will have you giggling ghoulishly! So get ready to hold on to your head or it might fall off when you start laughing!!!</p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;">Question</span>: Why did Dracula take cold medicine?<br />
<span style="color: #ff6600;">Answer</span>: To get rid of his coffin.</p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;">Question</span>:  What is a ghost’s favorite kind of road?<br />
<span style="color: #ff6600;">Answer</span>: Dead Ends.</p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;">Question</span>:  What kind of mistakes do ghosts make?<br />
<span style="color: #ff6600;">Answer</span>: Boo Boos</p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;">Question</span>: Where do spooks mail their letters?<br />
<span style="color: #ff6600;">Answer</span>:  At the Ghost Office</p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;">Question</span>: Who won the Skeleton Beauty Contest?<br />
<span style="color: #ff6600;">Answer</span>:  No body.</p>
<p>Head still connected? If not, then get yourself together and send us YOUR jokes too! Send them to <a href="mailto:usa_blog@ekoloko.com">usa_blog@ekoloko.com</a> and write the word “Jokes” in the subject of your mail, and don’t forget your Eko name.</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-14" title="rangers of the week header" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" alt="" width="625" height="62" /></a></p>
<p>Enjoy some pictures of our Advanced Rangers ceremony last week:</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/ceremony2.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-375" title="ceremony2" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/ceremony2.png" alt="" width="648" height="257" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/ceremony-donuts.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-374" title="ceremony donuts" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/ceremony-donuts.png" alt="" width="474" height="250" /></a></p>
<p>If you were supposed to be at the ceremony but couldn’t make it at the scheduled time, please talk to a manager and another date will be arranged for you.</p>
<p>This week’s ceremony for Advanced Rangers will take place on two different days.</p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #000080;">On Wednesday, October 31st, at 3:30 PM Eastern Time</span></strong> (9:30 Europe and Israel time) we will have Ido450, Ponpon5560 and maybe Taleko</p>
<p><span style="color: #000080;"><strong>On Thursday, November 1<sup>st</sup>, at 3:30 PM Eastern Time </strong></span>our worthy rangers who will be getting their Advanced Ranger halos are: DanApple, mrnaia, Finder92 and Linkeko</p>
<p>Finally – there are lots and lots of new Ekos who need your help.</p>
<p>We wanted to remind you that the <span style="color: #008000;"><strong>BEST WAY</strong></span> to offer help is by INVITING new Ekos to play games with you, inviting them to see your moon house and offering to visit their houses and show them how to farm, and offering to take them around to see ekoloko or do quests.</p>
<p>Running around saying “Who needs help? I’m here to help you,” over and over is NOT what we mean by helping.</p>
<p>So get out there all you rangers, and rangers to be…and let’s make ekoloko USA the greatest place in the world!</p>
				</div>
				<div class="clear"> </div>
                <div class="up-bottom-border">
				<p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=3" title="View all posts in EkoNews" rel="category">EkoNews</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=6" title="View all posts in Events" rel="category">Events</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=4" title="View all posts in LokoJokes" rel="category">LokoJokes</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=7" title="View all posts in Rangers" rel="category">Rangers</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=369#comments" title="Comment on The Halloween Event">15 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
				</div>
            
		                
                </div><!--close post class-->
	
				
			<div class="post-355 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-ekonews category-events">
				<p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on October 24, 2012</p>
                <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=355">Invasion of the Pumpkins &#8211; Part 2</a></h2>
				<div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>	
				<div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/spooky-event-title3.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-276" title="spooky event title3" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/spooky-event-title3.png" alt="" width="324" height="93" /></a></p>
<p>It’s official! Halloween has arrived in ekoloko!</p>
<p>Adam Greenleaf has called all Ekos to help fight the ghosts and goblins and other scary stuff that is going on in ekoloko…I mean, like what’s with all these PUMPKINS???</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/community-event1.png" ><img class="size-full wp-image-361 aligncenter" title="community event1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/community-event1.png" alt="" width="366" height="73" /></a></p>
<p>Click the <strong>Community Event button</strong> and join us to fight the evil pumpkins sent by Goliath Smog – you need to <span style="color: #ff6600;">shoot the pumpkins</span>, and <span style="color: #ff6600;">whack the pumpkins</span>…and make pumpkin pie! (Just kidding!)</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Along the way there will be some awesome Tricks and Treats – quests that will give you fun prizes or…tricky tricks. Help us reach our goal and you will get the ultimate treat!</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/news-title11.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-120" title="news title1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/news-title11.png" alt="" width="339" height="63" /></a></p>
<p>Be on the lookout for the Halloween goodie bags you find laying around ekoloko. These may help you along the way…and help you get some extra goodie treats, so make sure to pick them up! You’ll also be helping keep <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/goodie-bags.png" ><img class="alignright size-full wp-image-359" title="goodie bags" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/goodie-bags.png" alt="" width="240" height="63" /></a>ekoloko clean and green!</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Want to see some COOL Halloween goodie bags? Take a look at these:</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/trick-or-treat-1.jpg" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-358" title="trick or treat 1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/trick-or-treat-1.jpg" alt="" width="151" height="151" /></a><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/recycle-pumpkin-bag.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-356" title="recycle-pumpkin-bag" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/recycle-pumpkin-bag.png" alt="" width="124" height="159" /></a><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/trick-or-treat-3.jpg" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-357" title="trick or treat 3" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/trick-or-treat-3.jpg" alt="" width="158" height="158" /></a></p>
				</div>
				<div class="clear"> </div>
                <div class="up-bottom-border">
				<p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=3" title="View all posts in EkoNews" rel="category">EkoNews</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=6" title="View all posts in Events" rel="category">Events</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=355#comments" title="Comment on Invasion of the Pumpkins &#8211; Part 2">8 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
				</div>
            
		                
                </div><!--close post class-->
	
				
			<div class="post-319 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-contests category-ekonews category-events category-rangers">
				<p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on October 23, 2012</p>
                <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=319">Invasion of the Pumpkins</a></h2>
				<div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>	
				<div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/spooky-event-title3.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-276" title="spooky event title3" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/spooky-event-title3.png" alt="" width="324" height="93" /></a></p>
<p>The spooky stuff just keeps getting spookier. I’m sure you’ve all heard about the perpetual night in the Jungle. Ekos are bumping into each other and suddenly <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Halloween-pumpkin1.png" ><img class="size-full wp-image-264 alignleft" title="Halloween pumpkin" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Halloween-pumpkin1.png" alt="" width="175" height="133" /></a>discovering – pumpkins!!! They are everywhere, as are the ghosts – and such colorful ghosts too!  We are not sure how this will end but we do know that we will need your help if we are to get rid of all these ghosts, goblins and scary pumpkins!</p>
<p>There is talk that we will need to get everyone together to help us fight against the darkness. Will you be there when we need you?!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-14" title="rangers of the week header" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" alt="" width="625" height="62" /></a></p>
<p>Here are our newest Ekos worthy of becoming <strong>Rangers of the Week</strong>! Congratulations to:  <strong>Finder92, mrnaia, ido450, taleko, ponpon5560 and Linkeko</strong>!</p>
<p>Remember – ekoloko Rangers are friendly, helpful and kind – both to Ekos and Managers! Keep up the good work you guys! We are counting on you!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Finder92.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-325" title="Finder92" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Finder92.png" alt="" width="79" height="99" /></a><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/mrnaia.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-326" title="mrnaia" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/mrnaia.png" alt="" width="67" height="118" /></a><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/ido450.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-328" title="ido450" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/ido450.png" alt="" width="47" height="111" /></a><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/taleko.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-324" title="taleko" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/taleko.png" alt="" width="59" height="108" /></a><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/ponpon5560.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-327" title="ponpon5560" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/ponpon5560.png" alt="" width="49" height="133" /></a>  <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Linkeko.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-323" title="Linkeko" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Linkeko.png" alt="" width="47" height="102" /></a></p>
<p><span style="color: #ff6600;"><strong>NOTICE*NOTICE*NOTICE</strong></span>: ADVANCED RANGER CEREMONY this <strong>WEDNESDAY</strong>, October 24th, at 3:30 pm EST (Donuts, Biggerboss11, Migo71, DanApple, Mazaii, wmmars and Blueking1!)</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/contests1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-122" title="contests1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/contests1.png" alt="" width="312" height="50" /></a></p>
<p>As promised – here is your next challenge – and this one is REALLY COOL!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/collette.png" ><img class="alignleft  wp-image-338" title="collette" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/collette.png" alt="" width="168" height="153" /></a>In the spirit of dressing up, we want you all to become EKOLOKO FASHIONISTAS!!!!!</p>
<p>You need to create a new clothing <strong>item</strong>, <strong>outfit</strong> or <strong>accessory</strong> for your Ekos.  Send in your drawings or creations to us at <a href="mailto:usa_blog@ekoloko.com">usa_blog@ekoloko.com</a> – write your Eko name in the mail and write the word ‘Contest’ in the subject of your mail.</p>
<p><strong>The winning item will be created by our design team and added to the ekoloko Mall!!!!!</strong></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/news-title1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-13" title="news title1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/news-title1.png" alt="" width="349" height="104" /></a></p>
<p>Daily events are coming back!!! And this time it&#8217;s official:</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Introducing</span>:</p>
<ul>
<li>Moon Hopping Mondays</li>
<li>Trendy Tuesdays</li>
<li>Wacky Wednesdays</li>
</ul>
<p><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>Today</strong></span>: Get your wardrobes ready for some fashionable fun!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/games-title.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-286" title="games title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/games-title.png" alt="" width="321" height="60" /></a></p>
<p>And in case you were scratching your heads….here is the solution for the Where’s Izzy game:</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/FindIzzyRo_solution.jpg" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-343" title="FindIzzyRo_solution" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/FindIzzyRo_solution.jpg" alt="" width="823" height="436" /></a></p>
<p>Stay tuned for more fun games!</p>
				</div>
				<div class="clear"> </div>
                <div class="up-bottom-border">
				<p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=8" title="View all posts in Contests" rel="category">Contests</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=3" title="View all posts in EkoNews" rel="category">EkoNews</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=6" title="View all posts in Events" rel="category">Events</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=7" title="View all posts in Rangers" rel="category">Rangers</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=319#comments" title="Comment on Invasion of the Pumpkins">23 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
				</div>
            
		                
                </div><!--close post class-->
	
				
			<div class="post-275 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-contests category-ekonews category-events category-rangers">
				<p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on October 20, 2012</p>
                <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=275">Just a Bunch of Boos</a></h2>
				<div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>	
				<div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/spooky-event-title3.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-276" title="spooky event title3" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/spooky-event-title3.png" alt="" width="324" height="93" /></a></p>
<p>And it&#8217;s getting spookier and spookier&#8230;.groups of ghosts are being spotted all over ekoloko!!!!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Ghosts-picture.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-277" title="Ghosts picture" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Ghosts-picture.png" alt="" width="562" height="186" /></a></p>
<p>How can we be sure they are who they say they are? Where are all these ghosts coming from? Are they friend or foe? Only you can say for sure&#8230;.</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/news-title1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-13" title="news title1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/news-title1.png" alt="" width="349" height="104" /></a></p>
<p>The last couple of days we&#8217;ve been busy having ranger ceremonies and we just wanted to share some of the wonderful photos we took of these special occasions! Keep playing hard, being friendly, helping other Ekos and showing us how much you care about our community, and you too could become one of our ekoloko Advanced Rangers! But don&#8217;t forget to do your Green Ranger quests first.</p>
<p>To do your Green Ranger quests &#8211; remember, you need to be at least Level 6, and to have played for at least 6 days on ekoloko! Good luck <img src='http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif' alt=':)' class='wp-smiley' /> </p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Rangers-ceremony-101812.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-279" title="Rangers ceremony 101812" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Rangers-ceremony-101812.png" alt="" width="860" height="446" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/ceremony-kim.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-280" title="ceremony kim" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/ceremony-kim.png" alt="" width="677" height="381" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/ceremony-jasper.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-278" title="ceremony jasper" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/ceremony-jasper.png" alt="" width="811" height="462" /></a></p>
<p>Next week&#8217;s Advanced Ranger ceremony will be held on Wednesday, at 3:30 PM EST.</p>
<p>Our new Rangers of the Week will be announced on Tuesday. Good luck to all you Green Rangers out there! We are counting on you!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/games-title.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-286" title="games title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/games-title.png" alt="" width="321" height="60" /></a></p>
<p>Just another new corner we are trying out &#8212; this is NOT a contest &#8211; it&#8217;s just for fun&#8230;.and games. This time we&#8217;re doing OUR version of Where&#8217;s Waldo? Only this time you&#8217;re trying to find out Where&#8217;s IzzyRo? Maybe the ghosts got her&#8230;.YOU tell US!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/FindIzzyRo.jpg" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-287" title="FindIzzyRo" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/FindIzzyRo.jpg" alt="" width="914" height="484" /></a></p>
<p>So&#8230;.where&#8217;s Izzy? Can you find her? Let us know. <img src='http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif' alt=':)' class='wp-smiley' /> </p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/write-to-us-title1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-81" title="write to us title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/write-to-us-title1.png" alt="" width="238" height="90" /></a></p>
<p>And again&#8230;we are always happy to hear your ideas, suggestions, comments, feedback, and yes, even your complaints &#8212; within reason of course&#8230;so please write to us at usa_blog@ekoloko.com. If you have suggestions for how to make the blog better &#8211; we want to hear them! This blog is for YOU!</p>
				</div>
				<div class="clear"> </div>
                <div class="up-bottom-border">
				<p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=8" title="View all posts in Contests" rel="category">Contests</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=3" title="View all posts in EkoNews" rel="category">EkoNews</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=6" title="View all posts in Events" rel="category">Events</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=7" title="View all posts in Rangers" rel="category">Rangers</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=275#comments" title="Comment on Just a Bunch of Boos">13 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
				</div>
            
		                
                </div><!--close post class-->
	
				
			<div class="post-173 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-contests category-ekonews category-events category-rangers">
				<p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on October 15, 2012</p>
                <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=173">Spooky Stuff</a></h2>
				<div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>	
				<div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/spooky-event-title1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-174" title="spooky event title1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/spooky-event-title1.png" alt="" width="347" height="110" /></a></p>
<p>Lots of spooky stuff is going on in ekoloko this month…there are rumors that we are going to be infested with ghosts and other spooks – and that we are going to have a “Spook Fest”!!!!!!!! Do you want to get haunted? BOO! <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/ghost.png" ><img class="alignright size-full wp-image-175" title="ghost" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/ghost.png" alt="" width="73" height="100" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Halloween-pumpkin.png" ><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-176" title="Halloween pumpkin" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Halloween-pumpkin.png" alt="" width="175" height="133" /></a>Maybe we will be able to scare Goliath Smog and his evil gang away from ekoloko for good! Join us this weekend – it will be <em>frightfully fun</em>!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" ><img class="size-full wp-image-14 alignnone" title="rangers of the week header" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" alt="" width="625" height="62" /></a>This week we found another SIX Ekos worthy of becoming Rangers of the Week.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Congratulations:</span> Donuts, Biggerboss11, Migo71, DanApple, Mazaii, and Blueking1!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Donuts.png" ><img class="wp-image-183 alignnone" title="Donuts" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Donuts.png" alt="" width="59" height="128" /></a><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Biggerboss11.png" ><img class="wp-image-181 alignnone" title="Biggerboss11" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Biggerboss11.png" alt="" width="49" height="107" /></a><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Migo71.png" ><img class="wp-image-180 alignnone" title="Migo71" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Migo71.png" alt="" width="79" height="117" /></a><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/DanApple.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-179" title="DanApple" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/DanApple.png" alt="" width="53" height="129" /></a><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Mazaii1.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-182" title="Mazaii1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Mazaii1.png" alt="" width="77" height="110" /></a><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Blueking1.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-178" title="Blueking1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Blueking1.png" alt="" width="48" height="118" /></a></p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #ff6600;">NOTICE*NOTICE*NOTICE</span></strong>: This Thursday (Oct. 18) at 3:30 EST we will hold the Ranger ceremony for our <span style="color: #ff6600;">ADVANCED RANGERS</span>:  Gabk720, Jasper, Supercity, amit5000, Butterfly, Kim1234, Omriliz, markcool, and wmmars</p>
<p>Next week&#8217;s ceremony will be Wednesday, Oct. 24th.</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/contests1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-122" title="contests1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/contests1.png" alt="" width="312" height="50" /></a></p>
<p>Hey there Eko friends! The design contest is almost over – you have <span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>ONE MORE DAY</strong></span> to submit your designs for the Eko screen we posted last week! Don’t forget to send your designs to us at <a href="mailto:usa_blog@ekoloko.com">usa_blog@ekoloko.com</a> !</p>
<p>And speaking of contests, <strong>we have our winners </strong>for the restaurant moonhouse contest!!!<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline;">Congratulations</span>: Riki07, Goldstar, johnnytest, Dancing4lyfe, Cchen222, DanApple, facehole, gabk720, Omriliz, MSPhey, Mazaii and cooldavid12!!!!</p>
<p>Can we have fries with that?</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/mazaiimoon.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-193" title="mazaiimoon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/mazaiimoon-300x166.png" alt="" width="270" height="149" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/gabkmoon.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-204" title="gabkmoon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/gabkmoon-300x170.png" alt="" width="270" height="153" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/OmriMoon.jpg" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-197" title="OmriMoon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/OmriMoon-300x159.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="143" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/goldstarmoon.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-194" title="goldstarmoon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/goldstarmoon-300x185.png" alt="" width="270" height="167" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/faceholeMoon.jpg" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-195" title="faceholeMoon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/faceholeMoon-300x146.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="131" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Riki07Moon.jpg" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-196" title="Riki07Moon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Riki07Moon-300x157.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="141" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/JohnnytestMoon.jpg" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-199" title="JohnnytestMoon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/JohnnytestMoon-300x175.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="158" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Cchen222Moon.jpg" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-202" title="Cchen222Moon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Cchen222Moon-300x153.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="138" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/MSPheyMoon.jpg" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-198" title="MSPheyMoon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/MSPheyMoon-300x190.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="171" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/DancingMoon.jpg" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-200" title="DancingMoon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/DancingMoon-300x159.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="143" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/DanAppleMoon.jpg" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-201" title="DanAppleMoon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/DanAppleMoon-300x154.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="139" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/cooldavidmoon.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-203" title="cooldavidmoon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/cooldavidmoon-300x172.png" alt="" width="270" height="155" /></a></p>
				</div>
				<div class="clear"> </div>
                <div class="up-bottom-border">
				<p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=8" title="View all posts in Contests" rel="category">Contests</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=3" title="View all posts in EkoNews" rel="category">EkoNews</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=6" title="View all posts in Events" rel="category">Events</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=7" title="View all posts in Rangers" rel="category">Rangers</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=173#comments" title="Comment on Spooky Stuff">27 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
				</div>
            
		                
                </div><!--close post class-->
	
				
			<div class="post-130 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-ekonews category-lokostyle category-rangers category-recipes">
				<p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on October 11, 2012</p>
                <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=130">Rangers, Recipes and More</a></h2>
				<div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>	
				<div class="entrytext">
  <p>This post is all about our Ekos – our newest Rangers of the Week, Eko Recipes, and some new Eko looks! Get ready to read about what our EKOS are doing!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-14" title="rangers of the week header" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" alt="" width="625" height="62" /></a></p>
<p>As reported, this week we chose SIX new Ekos to be Rangers of the Week. Our Rangers are chosen for a variety of reasons – but mainly because they have shown their dedication and loyalty to the ekoloko community, and are friendly, kind and helpful – both to Ekos and Managers!</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">So here are our new Rangers of the Week: Kim1234, Butterfly, Amit5000,Supercity, Jasper and Gabk720!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/rangers-week-4.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-131" title="rangers week 4" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/rangers-week-4.png" alt="" width="518" height="168" /></a></p>
<p>Congratulations to you all! Continue to make us proud! Woohooooooo!</p>
<p><span style="color: #c71585;"><strong>NOTICE*NOTICE*NOTICE</strong>: </span>ADVANCED RANGER CEREMONY TODAY will be postponed and held together with the Advanced Rangers in <span style="color: #c71585;">next week&#8217;s</span> ceremony on Thursday, October 18th, at 3:30 pm EST.</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Recipes-title.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-109" title="Recipes title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Recipes-title.png" alt="" width="274" height="89" /></a></p>
<p>Here are some of the recipes we’ve received so far! YUM-MEE!</p>
<p>Don’t forget to try them at home – and make sure to have a grownup around if you’re not allowed to use the stove or oven alone.</p>
<p>Remember that food is always about sharing!  So keep sending in your favorite recipes!</p>
<p>Just write the word “Recipe” in the Subject of your mail, include your EKO NAME and send to <a href="mailto:usa_blog@ekoloko.com">usa_blog@ekoloko.com</a>!</p>
<p><span style="color: #993300;"><strong>Jim’s Chocoloco </strong><strong>by matan078</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Ingredients:</span></p>
<p>¼ package of chocolate<br />
2 spoons of honey<br />
2 cups of milk<br />
marshmallows</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Preparation:</span></p>
<p>Break the chocolate into small pieces and put in a cup<br />
Heat the milk and pour half a cup into the cup with the chocolate and the honey<br />
Still until you get a smooth mix<br />
Pour half of the mix into two mugs<br />
Divide the rest of the heated milk into the cups<br />
Place a marshmallow in each cup</p>
<p><span style="color: #993300;"><strong>Chocolate Mango Mousse </strong><strong>by idoXD1121</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Ingredients:</span></p>
<p>1 large mango<br />
8 ounces (200 gr) of quality dark chocolate<br />
Juice of 1/2 a large lemon<br />
1/2 can of coconut cream</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Preparation:</span></p>
<p>1. Cut the chocolate into chunks and melt them in a pot on low heat.<br />
2. While the chocolate melts, add the coconut cream and stir.<br />
3. Grind half the mango in a blender with the lemon juice.  Keep the rest of the mango on the side for serving.<br />
4. Add the chocolate and coconut cream mixture to the blender and blend again on medium speed.<br />
5. Transfer to serving glasses, cover and chill until mousse becomes firm.<br />
6. Decorate with slices of remaining mango and serve with ice cream.</p>
<p><strong>Mmmmm sounds yummy. Must try that at home!</strong></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/style-title1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-35" title="style title1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/style-title1.png" alt="" width="334" height="112" /></a></p>
<p>And don&#8217;t forget to check out what they&#8217;re wearing this FALL on ekoloko!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/maxwell1.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-144" title="maxwell1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/maxwell1.png" alt="" width="117" height="228" /></a>     <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/peaches.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-145" title="peaches" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/peaches.png" alt="" width="91" height="179" /></a>     <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/matan078.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-146" title="matan078" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/matan078.png" alt="" width="82" height="168" /></a></p>
				</div>
				<div class="clear"> </div>
                <div class="up-bottom-border">
				<p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=3" title="View all posts in EkoNews" rel="category">EkoNews</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=5" title="View all posts in LokoStyle" rel="category">LokoStyle</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=7" title="View all posts in Rangers" rel="category">Rangers</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=10" title="View all posts in Recipes" rel="category">Recipes</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=130#comments" title="Comment on Rangers, Recipes and More">14 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
				</div>
            
		                
                </div><!--close post class-->
	
				
			<div class="post-121 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-contests category-ekonews">
				<p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on October 10, 2012</p>
                <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=121">Contests Contests Contests</a></h2>
				<div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>	
				<div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/news-title11.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-120" title="news title1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/news-title11.png" alt="" width="339" height="63" /></a></p>
<p>Hey everyone! We are starting a contest corner here on the blog &#8211; winners will get KOKOS to spend on ekoloko &#8212; and perhaps an occasional surprise gift!</p>
<p>Suggestions for contests are also welcome &#8211; remember to send all suggestions to usa_blog@ekoloko.com!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/contests1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-122" title="contests1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/contests1.png" alt="" width="312" height="50" /></a></p>
<p>Our first contest idea was sent to us by Donuts! <strong>And here&#8217;s the idea</strong>: below is a screen taken from ekoloko &#8211; all those who want to participate, need to take the screen and do something to it &#8211; decorate it, add things, do some design changes, and then submit their new design to us here at the blog (see address above). The 5 best designs will be posted on the blog &#8211; and then our blog readers will get to decide on the winner!</p>
<p>So thanks again, Donuts!</p>
<p>And here is the screen:</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Design-a-screen.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-123" title="Design a screen" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Design-a-screen.png" alt="" width="963" height="549" /></a></p>
<p>Have fun! Looking forward to seeing what you come up with <img src='http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif' alt=':)' class='wp-smiley' /> </p>
				</div>
				<div class="clear"> </div>
                <div class="up-bottom-border">
				<p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=8" title="View all posts in Contests" rel="category">Contests</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=3" title="View all posts in EkoNews" rel="category">EkoNews</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=121#comments" title="Comment on Contests Contests Contests">12 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
				</div>
            
		                
                </div><!--close post class-->
	
				
			<div class="post-58 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-ekonews category-rangers">
				<p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on October 4, 2012</p>
                <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=58">Rangers Rangers Rangers</a></h2>
				<div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>	
				<div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/news-title1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-67" title="news title1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/news-title1.png" alt="" width="339" height="63" /></a></p>
<p>We are excited to announce that we will now be choosing 5-6 new rangers each week so keep working hard to be the best Green Rangers you can be!</p>
<p>Not a Green Ranger yet? Ekos who have reached Level 6 and have played for at least 6 days on ekoloko are eligible to become Green Rangers and join our Ranger team. If you meet these minimum requirements then click the Question Mark icon, click the link to apply for Green Rangers, and begin your Green Ranger Quests!</p>
<p>And remember: ekoloko Rangers are friendly, helpful and kind!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-14" title="rangers of the week header" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" alt="" width="625" height="62" /></a></p>
<p>Here is a reminder about how we choose our Advanced Rangers:</p>
<ol>
<li>A number of Ekos are chosen as Rangers of the Week each week (or so).</li>
<li>These Rangers get fiery halos for a week.</li>
<li>Their fire halos will be replaced with Ranger halos at a Ranger ceremony.</li>
</ol>
<p>And this week:</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/rangers-week-3.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-64" title="rangers week 3" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/rangers-week-3.png" alt="" width="525" height="264" /></a></p>
<p>Our most recent Ranger Ceremony was very exciting and we were happy to welcome some special guests: our &#8216;experienced&#8217; Advanced Rangers, Avrila and Dancing4lyfe&#8230;and our own manager numberone were all there to help us congratulate our new Advanced Rangers:</p>
<p><a style="text-align: center;" href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/advanced-rangers-ceremony-2b.png" ><img class=" wp-image-86 aligncenter" title="advanced rangers ceremony 2b" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/advanced-rangers-ceremony-2b.png" alt="" width="767" height="420" /></a></p>
<p>Echococat, iCandy, Facehole and Liluna. Woo hoo!!!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Interviews-title1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-66" title="Interviews title1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Interviews-title1.png" alt="" width="368" height="81" /></a></p>
<div>
<p>Eko Butterfly interviewed some of our newest Advanced Rangers! Here’s what they had to say!</p>
</div>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/iCandy.png" ><img class=" wp-image-68 alignleft" title="iCandy" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/iCandy.png" alt="" width="82" height="146" /></a></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;">   Hi <strong>iCandy</strong>!</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #800080;">    Hello</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;">    What’s up?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #800080;">    Great!</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;"> How do you feel after the ceremony?</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #800080;">Well it’s a great feeling because I am now more able to help</span></p>
<p>And how do you feel about becoming a ranger, after all the investment?</p>
<p><span style="color: #800080;">I worked really hard for it but now I have to work harder to prove I am worthy to be a ranger</span></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">A quick questionnaire</span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">:</span></p>
<p>A permanent resident you like most?</p>
<p><span style="color: #800080;">Blade</span></p>
<p>What&#8217;s your favorite animal?</p>
<p><span style="color: #800080;">Panda</span></p>
<p>What&#8217;s your favorite game?</p>
<p><span style="color: #800080;">It was the ‘Vet’ but now ‘Glass balls’</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/echococat.png" ><img class=" wp-image-77 alignleft" title="echococat" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/echococat.png" alt="" width="85" height="139" /></a></p>
<p>Hi <strong>Echococat</strong>!</p>
<p><span style="color: #3366ff;">   Hello butterfly</span></p>
<p>What&#8217;s up?</p>
<p><span style="color: #3366ff;">   Not much</span></p>
<p>How do you feel after the ceremony?</p>
<p><span style="color: #3366ff;">Just walking around; Kind of nervous, I feel like I have more responsibility<strong>.</strong><strong> </strong></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #3366ff;">I&#8217;m afraid to let everyone down.</span></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">A quick questionnaire</span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">:</span></p>
<p>A permanent resident you like most?</p>
<p><span style="color: #3366ff;">Hmmmm, Heathcliff</span></p>
<p>What&#8217;s your favorite animal?</p>
<p><span style="color: #3366ff;">The tiger</span></p>
<p>What&#8217;s your favorite game?</p>
<p><span style="color: #3366ff;">The digging game in the mine</span></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/write-to-us-title1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-81" title="write to us title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/write-to-us-title1.png" alt="" width="238" height="90" /></a></p>
<p>Got an idea for a post or blog corner? Want to contribute to our blog? Write to <a href="mailto:usa_blog@ekoloko.com">usa_blog@ekoloko.com</a> with any ideas, comments or suggestions you may have.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="clear"> </div>
                <div class="up-bottom-border">
				<p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=3" title="View all posts in EkoNews" rel="category">EkoNews</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=7" title="View all posts in Rangers" rel="category">Rangers</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=58#comments" title="Comment on Rangers Rangers Rangers">25 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
				</div>
            
		                
                </div><!--close post class-->
	
				
			<div class="post-5 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-ekonews category-events category-lokojokes category-rangers">
				<p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on October 2, 2012</p>
                <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=5">Very First Blog Post</a></h2>
				<div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>	
				<div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/news-title1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-13" title="news title1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/news-title1.png" alt="" width="349" height="104" /></a></p>
<p>Welcome to our very first blog! Here you’ll read about everything that’s cool and new and happenin’ on ekoloko, get to know your fellow Ekos and the Managers you love, and get some tips and tricks for living clean and green!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-14" title="rangers of the week header" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" alt="" width="625" height="62" /></a></p>
<p>We have begun the selection for Advanced Rangers and this is how it will work:</p>
<ol>
<li>A small number of Ekos will be chosen as our Rangers of the Week.</li>
<li>These Rangers will receive temporary fiery halos.</li>
<li>Their fire halos will be replaced with Ranger halos at a Ranger ceremony.</li>
</ol>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-week-1.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-15" title="rangers week 1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-week-1.png" alt="" width="218" height="107" /></a>  <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-week-2.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-16" title="rangers week 2" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-week-2.png" alt="" width="186" height="113" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/events-title1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-22" title="events title1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/events-title1.png" alt="" width="222" height="81" /></a></p>
<p><span style="color: #003366;"><strong>GIRLS vs BOYS!!!!!</strong></span></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/girlsvboys.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-23" title="girlsvboys" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/girlsvboys.png" alt="" width="505" height="169" /></a></p>
<p>In the first of a series of contests between the GIRLS and the BOYS, this time sending gifts back to the kids on Hetra – the winners are: THE BOYS!  You’ve made Charles so proud!!!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/jokes-title1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-24" title="jokes title1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/jokes-title1.png" alt="" width="250" height="87" /></a></p>
<p>Even Massaimara would agree that laughter is the best medicine! Share your jokes and riddles and keep them laughing! Send in your favorites jokes and riddles and we’ll share them here!</p>
<p>Write to <a href="mailto:usa_blog@ekoloko.com">usa_blog@ekoloko.com</a> – write ‘EkoJokes’ in the subject of your mail.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="clear"> </div>
                <div class="up-bottom-border">
				<p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=3" title="View all posts in EkoNews" rel="category">EkoNews</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=6" title="View all posts in Events" rel="category">Events</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=4" title="View all posts in LokoJokes" rel="category">LokoJokes</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=7" title="View all posts in Rangers" rel="category">Rangers</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=5#comments" title="Comment on Very First Blog Post">31 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
				</div>
            
		                
                </div><!--close post class-->
	
					
